hotel_name: Real Select Vacations at The Ritz-Carlton Waikiki
review_body: We had a great stay complete with a super sized king bed, well stocked kitchen and, a beautiful view of the beach. I wouldn’t hesitate to go back. It’s right in the heart of of Waikiki with shops and the beach in close proximity. Superb!

hotel_name: Real Select Vacations at The Ritz-Carlton Waikiki
review_body: Friends from california in town for a weekend and we had the best, most relaxing time. It was our first time in this location and we had big expectations since we used to stay at the Ritz suites and residences on Maui. We loved the suite, the service, and the convenience of the location. We had so much fun, we didn't even leave Waikiki.Highly recommend!
